Node.Description: Go to Procurement and sourcing > Purchase orders > All purchase orders.
Click New.
In the Vendor account field, type a value.
Click Yes.
In the Order type field, type a value.
In the Site field, type a value.
In the Warehouse field, type a value.
Click OK.
On the Action Pane, click Purchase.
In the list, mark the selected row.
In the Item number field, type a value.
In the Quantity field, enter a number.
Click Save.
Close the page.
Go to Procurement and sourcing > Purchase orders > Purchase order confirmation > Confirm purchase orders.
Click Add.
In the list, mark the selected row.
In the Purchase order field, enter or select a value.
Close the page.
In the Purchase order field, type a value.
Click OK.
